@startuml screen-flow
!theme plain
hide empty description
skinparam defaultFontName monospace

state "Landing" as L : TribeLanding\n(browse / create tribes)
state "Checking" as GC : GeoCheckingScreen\n(spinner)
state "Too Far" as TF : TooFarScreen\n(back button)
state "Kicked Out" as KO : KickedOutScreen\n(auto-dismiss 4 s)
state "Geo Required" as GD : GeoRequiredScreen\n(location denied)
state "Inner Circle" as I : InnerCircle\n(chat, threads, map)

[*]  --> L  : app load

L   --> GC  : tribe selected\n(join / shared link / auto-join)
GC  --> I   : dist ≤ 5 km
GC  --> TF  : dist > 5 km, first visit
GC  --> KO  : dist > 5 km, was confirmed inside
GC  --> GD  : permission denied

I   --> KO  : drifts outside 5 km\n(geoGate useMemo fires)
I   --> L   : manual leave

TF  --> L   : back button
KO  --> L   : dismiss / auto 4 s
GD  --> L   : back button

@enduml
